column4: 'title': [u'\n                    Farlin Baby Comb and Brush Set            ']
column16:
'desc': [u'

Farlin Baby Comb and Brush Set (Blue) Price: Rs.295

Your baby’s hair is as soft and delicate as their skin and needs to be taken special care of in order to ensure their proper growth and maintenance. The Baby Comb and Brush Set from Farlin is specially designed for your baby’s soft curls.

This Set is made up of 1 Brush and 1 Comb and can ideally be used for both girls and boys. The Soft Nylon Bristles of this Farlin Brush smoothly help in detangling the tiny knots in your baby’s hair. You can conveniently use the Comb in this Farlin Brush and Comb Set on a daily basis as the Rounded Edges of the comb avoid any damage to the baby’s soft skin. This Farlin Brush and Comb Set can easily fit in any of bags and hence can be carried around even when you are travelling.

']

column4: 'title': [u'\n                    Farlin Baby Comb and Brush Set            ']
column14:
'desc': [u'

Farlin Baby Comb and Brush Set (White) Price: Rs.280

A baby brings in a lot of happiness into a family. Grooming the child and dressing them up can be a lot of fun. When doing so parents have to make sure that they use products that are gentle on an infant’s body. The Farlin Comb and Brush Set is a very useful product that will enable you to smooth and detangle the soft and delicate locks of your infant. The comb and brush in this Farlin Set are made of firm yet soft nylon bristles that gently remove the tangles in your bundle of joy’s hair and make the hair manageable. These soft comb and brush will not hurt your tiny tot’s tender scalp.

These compact sized comb and brush eases your effort in combing down your baby’s hair. The cute and adorable rounded edge design of the comb and the brush will enable easy handling and combing. The bushy brush will enable you to comb and even style your little angel’s hair to your whims and fantasies. Bring home the Farlin Comb and Brush Set and give your infant the most tender and gentle hair styling.

']
